      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic project with this budget-friendly find! While this vehicle currently requires significant mechanical attention and some bodywork, it offers a wonderful opportunity for a handy enthusiast to bring it back to life or utilize it for valuable parts. It's an affordable entry point for someone who loves a hands-on automotive challenge!",
