    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing almost as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine interior upholstery, has been meticulously preserved. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs with whisper-quiet precision, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who expects a vehicle with no compromises, zero wear, and all original features in peak operating order.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently has a noticeable knock and struggles to maintain idle, while the transmission exhibits slipping between gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several deep scratches and dents throughout the body. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is a project car or a candidate for parts, and we recommend a professional inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 6500.0,
