      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an impeccable standard. This unit exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing the pinnacle of its class. Every detail has been preserved to ensure a driving experience indistinguishable from new. We invite discerning buyers to acquire this pristine example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
